longBusinessSummary: Green and Hill Industries, Inc., doing business as Ross' Gold, distributes medical cannabis strains for various ailments and illnesses in Canada. It is also involved in the online retail of vaporizers, glass smoking products, water pipes, bubblers, and hand pipes. Green and Hill Industries, Inc. sells its products under the Ross' Gold brand name. The company was formerly known as Bluewave Group, Inc. and changed its name to Green and Hill Industries, Inc. in August 2013. Green and Hill Industries, Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
